1:56 PM Prosecuting attorney Jillian Pfeifer in court for the State of Wisconsin. Defendant Shaunta A. Winkka in court. Pfeifer states has spoken to Defendant - there is a resolution - would like to set out. Court questions Defendant on non-appearance. Defendant states her driver's vehicle over heated. Pfeifer would like to complete today. Defendant is in agreement with offer. Court reads on waiver of counsel - waiver free and voluntary. defendant pleads no contest. Court reads on waiver of rights and tendering plea. Waiver free and voluntary.
